@page "/about"

@layout HeaderLayout

<section id="about" class="about sec-pad">
    <div class="main-container">
        <h2 class="heading heading-sec heading-sec__mb-med">
            <span class="heading-sec__main">About Me</span>
            <span class="heading-sec__sub">
                A quick introduction to who I am, what I build, and the
                technologies I work with.
            </span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="about__content">
            <div class="about__content-main">
                <h3 class="about__content-title">Get to know me!</h3>
                <div class="about__content-details">
                    <p class="about__content-details-para">
                        Hi, I am <strong>Tafadzwa Kahwai</strong>, a <strong>Systems Developer and Analyst</strong> based in Zimbabwe.
                        I build practical web, desktop, mobile, and business applications using Microsoft technologies, with a strong focus on clean workflows, reliable data handling, and user-friendly systems.
                    </p>
                    <p class="about__content-details-para">
                        I hold a BSc in Computer Science from the University of Zimbabwe and started my professional career in March 2020 as a junior QA Analyst and junior developer.
                        I currently work at Comarsoft Solutions, where I lead the development and maintenance of a pensions administration system and support the full project lifecycle from analysis and implementation to testing, deployment, and ongoing improvements.
                    </p>
                    <p class="about__content-details-para">
                        My experience covers .NET, SQL, APIs, reporting, and modern application development.
                        Whether I am building a new system, improving an existing product, or supporting a live project, my goal is to deliver software that is efficient, maintainable, and useful to the people who rely on it.
                    </p>
                    <p class="about__content-details-para">
                        I am open to opportunities where I can contribute, learn, and grow. Connect with me on <a rel="noreferrer"
                                                                                                                      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tafadzwakahwai/"
                                                                                                                      target="_blank">Linkedin</a> or contact me on <a target="_blank"
                                                                                                                                                                       rel="noreferrer"
                                                                                                                                                                       href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=263784706556">
                            WhatsApp

                        </a> for consultations or collaborations.
                        If you have a suitable opportunity that aligns with my skills and experience, please reach out.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a href="contact" class="btn btn--med btn--theme dynamicBgClr">Contact</a>
            </div>
            <div class="about__content-skills">
                <h3 class="about__content-title">My Skills</h3>
                <SkillsList />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
